VERSION 1
WHEN FILE_NAME_IS Info.plist
WHEN CURRENT_FILE_MATCHES /NSAllowsArbitraryLoads\s*<\/key>\s*<true\s*\/>/i
OBSERVE PROJECT_HAS_GLOB **/*.plist AS plist_files
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON ATS arbitrary loads remain review-worthy even when other plist exceptions exist; project plist artifacts were inspected for context.
TRACE Mobile RDL pilot evaluated the Info.plist transport exception and recorded related project plist files for review context.
